'''詹姆士·史密斯·達許納'''（James Smith Dashner，1972年11月26日-）是一位美国儿童、青少年文学作家，主要代表作有 13th Reality 和《移动迷宫》系列<ref>{{cite web |url= http://jamesdashner.blogspot.com/2008/02/great-news-from-borders-bookstores.html |title= Great News from Borders Bookstores |work= jamesdashner.com |author= James Dashner |access-date= 2014-10-28 |archive-date= 2013-12-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131203001129/http://jamesdashner.blogspot.com/2008/02/great-news-from-borders-bookstores.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

== 生平 ==

達許納于1972年11月26日生于美国[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]的Austell，父母育有六个子女。先后毕业于 Duluth High School 和[[杨百翰大学|杨百翰大学]]的[[会计学|会计学]]专业<ref>{{cite news|last1=Stettler|first1=Jeremiah|title=Quitting his day job|url=http://www.sltrib.com/valleywest/ci_8477104|accessdate=15 October 2014|work=Salt Lake Tribune|date=6 Mar 2008|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141019110637/http://www.sltrib.com/valleywest/ci_8477104|archivedate=2014年10月19日}}</ref>。

他和妻子Lynette育有四个子女<ref>{{cite news|last1=Vice|first1=Jeff|title=James Dashner hits it big with series|url=http://www.deseretnews.com/article/705377839/James-Dashner-hits-it-big-with-series.html?pg=all|work=Deseret News|date=23 April 2010|accessdate=2014-10-28|archive-date=2019-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616114657/https://www.deseretnews.com/article/705377839/James-Dashner-hits-it-big-with-series.html?pg=all|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==著作==
達許納的作品主要面向青少年，类型包括冒险、生存和科幻领域。

其中《[[移动迷宫|移动迷宫]]》系列是他最知名的作品，曾在[[纽约时报畅销书榜|纽约时报畅销书榜]]上持续热销100周之久<ref>{{cite news|title=Best Sellers > Series Books|url=http://www.nytimes.com/best-sellers-books/2014-09-21/series-books/list.html|work=The New York Times Book Review|date=21 September 2014|accessdate=2014-10-28|archive-date=2016-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323012630/http://www.nytimes.com/best-sellers-books/2014-09-21/series-books/list.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，全系列都改編成電影。

